  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Human Resource Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Handle end-to-end recruitment and hiring processes</li><li>Prepare workers employment contracts and HR documentation</li><li>Process monthly payroll and statutory submissions</li><li>Maintain and update employee personnel files (P-files)</li><li>Track and update training records and certifications</li><li>Respond to employee HR enquiries and provide daily HR support</li><li>Ensure compliance with company policies and employment regulations</li><li>Support HR administration, reporting, and audits</li><li>Perform ad-hoc HR duties as assigned by Management</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Human Resources</li><li>Minimum 2–3 years of HR or relevant administrative experience</li><li>Basic knowledge of Singapore Employment Act and HR practices</li><li>Experience in recruitment, payroll, and personnel records management preferred</li><li>Proficient in MS Office and HR systems</li><li>Detail-oriented, well-organised, and able to handle confidential information</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Ability to multitask and work independently with minimal supervision</li></ul>",
